title: Carole Baskin: Authorities seek new leads in unsolved disappearance of Tiger King star's husband
description: Sheriff credits Netflix show with sparking new interest in the case
content:
Authorities in Florida are making a fresh appeal for help in the unsolved disappearance of Jack Donald Lewis, the husband of Tiger Kings Carole Baskin.
